00:32:23.700 --> 00:32:27.620
And I think, yeah, I've often seen like unit tests pass

00:32:27.630 --> 00:32:29.560
and say, I mean, there's like lots of memes about this, right?

00:32:29.630 --> 00:32:31.520
How like unit tests say everything is good,

00:32:31.650 --> 00:32:32.500
but the server is down.

00:32:32.590 --> 00:32:33.320
